    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Minor updates:<br>- Fixed the bug in connecting to a remote host, basically it wasn't working.<br>- NtsSetHost is now global, so you don't have to open the window before<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;switching to a remote host.<br>- Check and not load if it is not windows (David Fishburn).<br></td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="rowodd" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=2682">ntservices.vim</a></td>
    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" nowrap><b>1.5</b></td>
    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" nowrap><i>2004-01-27</i></td>
