    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">With the help of David Fishburn, I was able to identify a problem and fix it. I also added a command and &lt;Plug&gt; mapping to activate the window without needing WinManager at all (for those who don't want to install WinManager). Thanks a lot to David for debugging the problem and providing help in other ways too.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
        <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><a href="download_script.php?src_id=1644">ntservices.vim</a></td>
