    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Cscript wasn't executing vbscripts on some machines unless the //E:vbscript option is passed. If it still doesn't work for you, please do me a favour by running cscript manually on the temp file created with the .vbs extension in the temp directory like this:<br><br>cscript //E:vbscript //Nologo &lt;temp file created by plugin&gt;<br><br>and please report the error that you see. Thank you.</td>
